      <title>摩根士丹利大宗交易泄密事件令黑石集团和橡树资本集团蒙受损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/blackstone-oaktree-burned-by-morgan-stanley-s-block-trade-leaks</link>
