    <item>
      <title>罗格夫认为，如果经济保持稳定，美联储六次降息只是“白日梦”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/davos-2024-rogoff-sees-six-fed-rate-cuts-as-pipedream-if-economy-holds-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈佛大学教授肯尼思·罗格夫 (Kenneth Rogoff) 表示，除非美国以某种方式陷入“深度衰退”，否则美联储不会实施交易员押注的 2024 年六次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/davos-2024-rogoff-sees-six-fed-rate-cuts-as-pipedream-if-economy-holds-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 11:40:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
