    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行的转变令德国投资者前景意外改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/german-investor-outlook-unexpectedly-improves-for-sixth-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国投资者前景出人意料地连续第六个月改善，因为人们希望货币宽松政策将帮助欧洲最大经济体从去年底的收缩中反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/german-investor-outlook-unexpectedly-improves-for-sixth-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:05:59 GMT</pubDate>
